value.string: Walaka Maui is Kihei's hidden gem and seldom available. Located up at the top of hte hill, it commands grace and elegance. It's a newer building built in 2006, this ground floor unit boasts interior features of granite counter tops and stainless steel appliances in the kitchen, a built-in murphy bed, bookcases and much more. There is a separate storage area for all your Maui toys, and 2 parking spaces. The beautiful garden and mountain view is both relaxing and contemplative. Celebrate the Maui lifestyle here at Walaka Maui. Don't miss this opportunity, call an agent today!
